title: ULC stamp typeface
content:
anybody know what this is? the closest i came was Trade Gothic LT Std Cn, Bold. but i know it's not the right one.

does anybody know what it is or what a close substitute may be?

thanks in advance.

 ![](http://web.archive.org/web/20130426061548im_/http:/typophile.com/files/ULC_logo.jpg)
author: Kenny Bania

comments.content: [Univers 59 Ultra Condensed](http://web.archive.org/web/20130426061548/http:/www.myfonts.com/fonts/linotype/univers/59-ultra-condensed/) is probably a closer match.

looks more like [DIN](http://web.archive.org/web/20130426061548/http:/www.fontshop.com/index.cfm?fuseaction=catalog.fontpackage&startrow=1&records=&currpage=1&totalrecords=4&displayfontid=EF.6759.0.0&fontRendererText=ULC) to me.
